data.description: Welcome home to one of the most convenient, centrally located homes in a perfect family neighborhood that you are likely to find. Less than 10 minutes to the World Class Market Commons with shopping, restaurants, playgrounds, and athletic fields or to the best major regional mall in the area. Less than 15 minutes to multiple beach access points. The home could really not be much more centrally located and it is east of the ICW. Large open floorplan that makes the home feel even larger than it is. Beautiful upgrade granite counter tops including the island with sink!! Oversized garage, large master suite, and good sized secondary bedrooms make this the perfect family home. One of the most popular floorplans around!!! Newer Roof and HVAC upgrades!! Add to that a full yard sprinkler system and have a low maintenance property that you and your family will be proud to call home for many years to come!!!
